# Electron Desktop Pet Window

## Asset Source

Desktop window displays `pet.png` (rembg-processed transparent PNG) — never `minimax_raw` or user original.

## Window Spec (MVP)

- `frame: false`, `transparent: true`, `alwaysOnTop: true` (toggleable)
- Default height 160px; presets 120 / 160 / 220
- Click-through: post-MVP

## Required Behaviors

- Drag + persist position; right-click menu; hide / quit
- Display single pose image; **all states via CSS animation** (no multi-pose swap in MVP)

## Pet States → Animation (same image)

| State | Animation |
|-------|-----------|
| idle | gentle float |
| happy | side sway |
| sleep | lower opacity + Zzz bubble |
| focus | breathing |
| remind | bounce |
| angry | brief shake |

Post-MVP: optional idle/happy/sleep/focus image sets — do not scaffold unless asked.

## Multi-Window

- Pet overlay window + separate control/onboarding windows
- Do not embed onboarding in pet window

## Platform

- macOS first if primary dev machine; validate transparent PNG rendering per OS
